003e\u003c/p\u003e\u003c/div\u003e\u003cp\u003eCompleting the first Trials of Aql in \u003cem\u003eDune: Awakening\u003c/em\u003e is part of the main quest. During the \u003cstrong\u003eEchoes from the Past\u003c/strong\u003e main quest, you need to find the entrance to the altar. You find the first trial on the \u003cstrong\u003elargest rock formation in the South part of Hagga Basin South\u003c/strong\u003e.\u003c/p\u003e\u003cdiv\u003e\u003cdiv\u003e\u003cp\u003e\u003ca href=\"https://platform.polygon.com/wp-content/uploads/sites/2/2025/06/duneawakening_guide_trials_first_entrance.jpg?quality=90\u0026amp;strip=all\u0026amp;crop=0,0,100,100\" data-pswp-height=\"1080\" data-pswp-width=\"1920\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer\"\u003e\u003cimg alt=\"A montage of two Dunge: Awakening screenshots showing the path to the entrance of the first Trial of Aql.\" data-chromatic=\"ignore\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" data-nimg=\"fill\" sizes=\"(max-width: 639px) 100vw, (max-width: 1023px) 50vw, 700px\" srcset=\"https://platform.polygon.com/wp-content/uploads/sites/2/2025/06/duneawakening_guide_trials_first_entrance.jpg?quality=90\u0026amp;strip=all\u0026amp;crop=0%2C0%2C100%2C100\u0026amp;w=256 256w, https://platform.polygon.com/wp-content/uploads/sites/2/2025/06/duneawakening_guide_trials_first_entrance.jpg?quality=90\u0026amp;strip=all\u0026amp;crop=0%2C0%2C100%2C100\u0026amp;w=376 376w, https://platform.polygon.com/wp-content/uploads/sites/2/2025/06/duneawakening_guide_trials_first_entrance.jpg?quality=90\u0026amp;strip=all\u0026amp;crop=0%2C0%2C100%2C100\u0026amp;w=384 384w, https://platform.polygon.com/wp-content/uploads/sites/2/2025/06/duneawakening_guide_trials_first_entrance.jpg?quality=90\u0026amp;strip=all\u0026amp;crop=0%2C0%2C100%2C100\u0026amp;w=415 415w, https://platform.polygon.com/wp-content/uploads/sites/2/2025/06/duneawakening_guide_trials_first_entrance.jpg?quality=90\u0026amp;strip=all\u0026amp;crop=0%2C0%2C100%2C100\u0026amp;w=480 480w, https:/